{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b1",
      "translation": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b2",
      "translation": "Group Chief Executive Officer and President's Report"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b3",
      "translation": "2020 Performance Summary"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b4",
      "translation": "AIA's China business made the largest contribution to the Group's new business value in 2020 and performed excellently in early 2021, compared with the same period in 2020,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b5",
      "translation": "the first two months of this year recorded very strong new business value growth. Although 2020 new business value of USD 968 million declined 17% from 2019, this was primarily"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b6",
      "translation": "due to limited new sales in the first quarter following the initial outbreak of COVID-19. Operating profit after tax grew 14% during the year, mainly driven by our growing"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b7",
      "translation": "in-force policy portfolio and favorable claims experience."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b8",
      "translation": "In 2020, we successfully obtained regulatory approval to convert our Shanghai branch into China's first wholly foreign-owned life insurance subsidiary. In March 2021,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b9",
      "translation": "we received approval from the China Banking and Insurance Regulatory Commission to commence operations in Sichuan Province. Sichuan is China's sixth largest province by GDP"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b10",
      "translation": "and fourth largest by population, presenting significant long-term growth opportunities for AIA."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b11",
      "translation": "Hong Kong implemented travel restrictions in early February 2020, effectively halting new business sales from mainland Chinese visitors, resulting in a significant decline in new business value."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b12",
      "translation": "Compared with the first half, our agent distribution channel achieved double-digit sales growth from local customers in the second half, maintaining a significant market"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b13",
      "translation": "leadership position. Partner distribution channel new business value was significantly lower than 2019, primarily due to the higher historical sales proportion from mainland Chinese visitors through the retail independent financial advisor channel."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b14",
      "translation": "Operating profit after tax grew 10%, benefiting from strong renewal premium growth and favorable claims experience."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b15",
      "translation": "AIA's Thailand business recorded very strong performance in the second half. Although new business value declined 4% for the full year, as movement restrictions eased, monthly"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b16",
      "translation": "performance showed positive momentum, with second half new business value up 33% from the first half."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b17",
      "translation": "Singapore business also showed excellent improvement in the second half, with new business value up 56% compared with the first half and up 12% year-on-year. Full year new business value"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b18",
      "translation": "declined 5%, as our overseas partner business was impacted by strict border control measures, offsetting agent channel growth. Operating profit after tax rose"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b19",
      "translation": "8%."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b20",
      "translation": "In Malaysia, new business value declined 13% for the full year, particularly reflecting strict movement restrictions in the first half. Second half new business value recovered, up"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b21",
      "translation": "72% from the first half."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b22",
      "translation": "In other markets, second half new business value rose 10% from the first half, with positive recoveries in South Korea and Indonesia. Overall, new business value"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b23",
      "translation": "declined 4% for the full year, mainly due to declines in New Zealand, the Philippines and Indonesia. Other markets recorded positive new business value growth, including Vietnam,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b24",
      "translation": "Taiwan and India, which achieved double-digit growth in 2020 compared with 2019."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b25",
      "translation": "On the agent channel, we shifted to online recruitment and onboarding, supporting double-digit growth in newly recruited agents and agent managers."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b26",
      "translation": "Although face-to-face meetings were restricted during the pandemic, resulting in a 28% decline in new business value, as restrictions eased and businesses adopted new digital"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b27",
      "translation": "tools, new business value rebounded strongly in the second half. Positive sales momentum continued into 2021, with agent business recording very strong new business value growth in the first two"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b28",
      "translation": "months compared with the same period in 2020."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b29",
      "translation": "Travel restrictions on mainland Chinese visitors to Hong Kong impacted our retail independent financial advisor business, resulting in a 41% decline in partner channel new business value"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b30",
      "translation": "in 2020. We benefited from more resilient bancassurance performance, which contributed the majority of new business value for this channel. Our bancassurance partnerships with Indonesia's Bank"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b31",
      "translation": "Central Asia (BCA), Thailand's Bangkok Bank Public Company Limited and Malaysia's Public Bank"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b32",
      "translation": "Berhad all recorded positive new business value growth in 2020."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p14_b33",
      "translation": "012\nAIA Group Limited"
    }
  ]
}
```
